---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About · Nicolás Andrés Calvo" description="Cloud / DevOps engineer.">
  <section class="section">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        I'm <strong>Nicolás Andrés Calvo</strong>, a Cloud / DevOps engineer. I work on AWS, ECS Fargate,
        Terraform and Kubernetes, building infrastructure that is stateless, disposable and
        observable, and migrating systems that aren't yet.
      </p>
      <p>
        This site collects case studies from real engagements: the context, the architecture, the
        decisions I made and what they cost. Names and figures in the public write-ups are
        generalized; the goal is to show how I reason, not to leak anyone's internals.
      </p>
      <h3>Find me</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/NicolasAndresCalvo">GitHub</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/nicolas-andres-calvo/">LinkedIn</a></li>
        <li><a href="/cv.pdf">Download CV (PDF)</a></li>
      </ul>
      <p style="color:var(--fg-muted);font-size:.9rem">
        (CV link is a placeholder, drop <code>cv.pdf</code> into <code>public/</code> to enable it.)
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
